      "date": "2013-09-17 15:13:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nIf I try to enable both policies in a single write then only the last policy in the list is enabled:\n\n t:~# echo NonBlockingRestore > /proc/fs/lustre/mdt/lustre-MDT0000/hsm/policy\n t:~# cat /proc/fs/lustre/mdt/lustre-MDT0000/hsm/policy\n [NonBlockingRestore] NoRetryAction\n t:~# echo NonBlockingRestore NoRetryAction > /proc/fs/lustre/mdt/lustre-MDT0000/hsm/policy\n t:~# cat /proc/fs/lustre/mdt/lustre-MDT0000 /hsm/policyNonBlockingRestore [NoRetryAction]",
