    {
      "id": "7f8f95a57ef77d098fb5aa781804e4c1b3a0db3e",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 140,
        "name": "jacques-Charles Lafoucriere",
        "email": "jacques-charles.lafoucriere@cea.fr",
        "username": "jcl"
      },
      "date": "2013-09-18 07:54:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nThe logic is + to add, - to remove, none to overide\nSo when you do:\n t:~# echo NonBlockingRestore NoRetryAction > /proc/fs/lustre/mdt/lustre-MDT0000/hsm/policy\nthis is understood as overide + overide so only the last one remind. I will change it so a more logical way to use it",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "ae6c1bd47928664d8f7a868c10d67aca848df3bb",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 140,
        "name": "jacques-Charles Lafoucriere",
        "email": "jacques-charles.lafoucriere@cea.fr",
        "username": "jcl"
      },
      "date": "2013-09-18 08:04:01.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nThe new logic:",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "af881602f3748796789380f7452829ab7701c4a6",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 140,
        "name": "jacques-Charles Lafoucriere",
        "email": "jacques-charles.lafoucriere@cea.fr",
        "username": "jcl"
      },
      "date": "2013-09-18 08:10:18.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nSorry (wrong kbd combinaison):\nNew logic:\n-- +P1 +P2: add P1 and P2\n-- +P1 -P2: add P1 remove P2\n-- P1 P2: set to P1 and P2\n-- P1 -P2: set to P1 remove P2 => result is P1\n-- -P1 P2: remove P1 add P2 \nI can also forbid a mix of P and +/-P so 4 and 5 forbidden",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "da50270c7198ff319d3d3b138f2d2674a3cfe746",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 147,
        "name": "Maloo",
        "email": "maloo@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "maloo",
        "tags": [
          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2013-09-18 10:50:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nRosso Autotest has started the test process",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "f287e1d2ce68b5b0dff6de4a5d882056c04b6bb8",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 177,
        "name": "John Hammond",
        "email": "jhammond@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "jhammond"
      },
      "date": "2013-09-18 18:02:31.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n> New logic: -- +P1 +P2: add P1 and P2 -- +P1 -P2: add P1 remove P2 -- P1 P2: set to P1 and P2 -- P1 -P2: set to P1 remove P2 => result is P1 -- -P1 P2: remove P1 add P2 I can also forbid a mix of P and +/-P so 4 and 5 forbidden\n\nSGTM. But it seems that the logic is unchanged from patch set 3 to 4. Will you push a new patch?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "88a950f9ffdd112456b87cebad841a5bd17d3197",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 147,
        "name": "Maloo",
        "email": "maloo@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "maloo",
        "tags": [
          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2013-09-18 20:28:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/271fdb16-209a-11e3-b9bc-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
